en-US.summary: Listen to STAR 93.3 Uplifting and Encouraging Radio
examplePhrases: Alexa, open STAR Ninety Three Three
Alexa, play STAR Ninety Three Three
Alexa, ask STAR Ninety Three Three to play
en-US.name: STAR Ninety Three Three
en-US.description:
Listen to STAR 93.3

STAR 93.3 provides Uplifting and Encouraging Radio 24/7.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch STAR Ninety Three Three" or "Alexa, play STAR Ninety Three Three" to start the radio".

At anytime, you can stop the radio by saying "Alexa, stop"
